------------------Mythbuntu Control Panel------------------

Mythbuntu Control Panel (MCP) is a modified version of Mythbuntu Control Centre
Copyright (C) 2020  Ted (MythTV Forums member heyted)
MCP is used to install and configure MythTV on Ubuntu.
MCP source code: https://github.com/mythcp/mythbuntu-control-panel

